<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />

    <style>
      * {
        font-family: -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', 'PingFang SC', 'Hiragino Sans GB', 'Microsoft YaHei', 'Helvetica Neue', Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol';
        font-weight: 300;
        box-sizing: border-box;
        color: #46454c;
      }

      .header {
        background-color: #a6905b;
        padding: .8rem 2rem;
      }

      .email-container {
        max-width: 900px;
        background-color: #fbfbfb;
        margin: auto;
        box-shadow: 0px 5px 5px 2px #46454c45;
      }

      .email-body-container {
        padding: 2rem;
      }

      .big {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: 1.5rem;
        color: #fbfbfb;
      }

      b {
        font-weight: 400;
      }

      a {
        color: #71a4ea;
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      hr {
        margin: 2rem 0;
        opacity: .5;
      }
    </style>
  </head>

  <body>
    <div class="email-container">
      <div class="header">
        <h1>Sorry, we cannot grant you access to Brittle Pins at the moment</h1>
      </div>

      <div class="email-body-container">
        <p>
          You requested an invitation to <b>Brittle Pins</b> for the email address <b><%= @email %></b>.
          Unfortunately, access cannot be provided at the moment.
        </p>

        <p>
          If you believe this rejection is a mistake, you can
          <a href="mailto:admin@brittle-pins.com?subject=Access denied">contact our admin</a>.
        </p>

        <p>
          Keep in mind that the service is currently working in a closed testing mode, and is not yet open for the general public.
          Please get in touch with us before you send another request.
        </p>

        <hr />

        <small>
          Please don't reply directly to this email.
          Instead, you can <a href="mailto:admin@brittle-pins.com?subject=Access denied">contact our admin</a>.
        </small>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>